➜6070后的问候语是“吃了没”，而9000后却用“拉屎没”打招呼？
http://www.sohu.com/a/410404769_425113	41114
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200729/37eb9f53c15441b9848719733f2d9d4e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200729/9f8194ff88114d639970c07268a21e86.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果你打开写给外国人的汉语教材</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">99%都会有问候语教学：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你好/您好/你好吗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200729/8d948615af2445c58f6e035b9c2981ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">然而大家都知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在现实生活中的大部分场合</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中国人见面打招呼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实都并不会用“你好”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200729/5207ae0b41e44fd3830ff7e72af505ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至每个地方的问候语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也大不相同</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里面的门道之多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有时候甚至连我们自个儿也道不明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>下面就跟着文字君一起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>来初步探索一下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>各个地方都有哪些有趣的问候语吧~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200729/e12c7b9e4fbf47d0bb05ca7b4b7a8e52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在人们还没反应过来的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">新型冠状病毒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就以迅雷不及掩耳之势改变了一切</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家的生活天翻地覆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打招呼的方式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也迅速发生了改变</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为要防止感染</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肢体接触首先要被避免</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">握手拥抱亲脸颊都是高危动作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这种情况下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">穿着鞋碰碰脚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仿佛也能象征性的代表一种关怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200729/99b9fb1cf60c48218831dcda7b46c552.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这反倒让新时代的社恐青年们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感到了由衷的幸福…</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200729/2a65e110cf3d4a978c8600e58638b3a5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肢体接触没有了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问候语当然也要随之改变</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以前北京人见面问</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“吃饭了么您内？ ”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在全城核酸检测</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“核酸了么您内？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就显得更加应景了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200729/8ca4bd3079cd48e9a3699532c120b75d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而往年过年都会说的”恭喜发财“</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不如”<strong>百毒不侵</strong>“更合适</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200729/520339d3309c4189996b14edea6f65e4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算是在新冠期间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问候语也是有一个发展变化过程的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最开始是：口罩还够吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后是：你们单位上班了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而发展到 “核酸了吗您内 ”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都已经是几个月以后的事情了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今电影院终于开张</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文字君大胆预测</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下一波流行的问候语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">估计是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“去看电影了吗？”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200729/c864cfdd9abc4966b0251b9e728eb417.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200729/56366f90bbc040a6a4570368c7356ba4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200729/8adcea82ed5a42cda9787df639758865.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问候语不仅会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随着时间、事件改变</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不同地方的人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打招呼的方式也不一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200729/6f1a3532b1614a19b26642c3e61ed6d8.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">北京人会祭出热情的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>倒装句三连</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<strong>吃了么您？</strong>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<strong>上哪去啊您这是？</strong>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<strong>最近咋样啊您？</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">不由得让人产生一种哲学的思考</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我是谁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我从哪儿来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我要去哪儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200729/8cbb9432f999405abedaf785e5f7e7f8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而四川人微微一笑</p>
<blockquote>
<strong>幺妹儿，逛街去？</strong>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<strong>今天安逸了吗？</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">天府之国，安逸最重要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有什么能让四川人放弃安逸吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不可能！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四川人的打招呼是就事论事的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">处于什么状态就打什么招呼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逛街吃饭看电影皆可用上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但有时候也会出现一些尴尬场面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">”大哥，你也来上厕所呀？“</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200729/4215dc786b0b4335ad7ee42a56058812.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到了上海，那就不得了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个疫情时期还在坚持垃圾分类的城市</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管是徐汇名媛还是金桥码农</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总归免不了这一句灵魂拷问</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>”你是什么垃圾！“</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以每个上海市民</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都熟知垃圾分类原则</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湿巾再湿都是干垃圾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瓜子皮再干都是湿垃圾</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200729/f4dae4ee7c0c489bb2626bfb10ed55ad.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">耿直的东北人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才不会搞那么多花样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人家连假装问你吃没吃都放弃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直接上来就一句<strong>“嘎哈呢！”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">什么哥哥妹妹姐姐弟弟之类的称呼？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不存在！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">普天之下莫非王土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">率土之滨莫非老铁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200729/d8411658c08d4b2491a70aac4071590b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于山东人，尤其是济南人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们那里的一种地方特色</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今已被全国网友发扬光大了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——见人就叫老师</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<strong>老师，苹果多少钱一斤？</strong>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<strong>老师， 大明湖畔有夏雨荷吗？</strong>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<strong>老师，你大孙子高考考咋样？</strong>
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然在我国其他地区</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们不用”老师“来打招呼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但是他们热衷于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>管一切不是老师的人叫老师</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如理发店的Tony老师</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">房地产中介小王老师</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保险经纪崔西老师</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至楼下的家政服务</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">老板也是大沈老师</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200729/9c6aed6de427471e8f51a018e4e8823f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拿不准管人叫什么？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来个老师准没错！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200729/5cced9f754324da5998c24f05c396d36.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前面我们说的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还都是三次元的真实问候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而到了网络世界里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问候语就变得更加放飞自我了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200729/08b7b931ded04a96be8998b97ceeb4bd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以前人们爱用“吃了吗 ”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为问候语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是因为大家都为吃饱饭发愁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">娱乐活动也相对匮乏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今物质条件越来越丰足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们想要的东西</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也从生理需求上升到了<strong>社交需求</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问候语也随之改变</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更加关注情感色彩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200729/7423f3e8d1494b609cdc7f79e6ddd961.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在现实世界中可能还要考虑到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">约定俗成的规矩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可是到了没人认识你的社交软件上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家的问候语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就变得愈发<strong>个性化</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200729/eee6b952e9094136b803dfc55f93cab8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天你暴躁了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天你喝奶茶了吗?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天你家的猫尿床了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天你舔狗了吗？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>”今天......了吗“ 句式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用来直戳肺管子真是再合适不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200729/a6abb37094984a42ad38e642758acaa9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种句式虽然直白</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但也间接彰显了与某个人之间的<strong>熟悉度</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相比“吃了吗”这种浅显的问候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更能体现出真切的关怀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如与对象或者闺蜜铁汁之间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最常说的话恐怕就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“今天你拉屎了吗”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“在拉屎”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“准备去拉屎”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尽管听起来不太雅观</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但却实实在在表达了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对对方的关心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟拉屎这件事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能反应出一个人的身心健康</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200729/682565cbc3b648c7b4c2bb0d16ba700b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要说起讨人厌的问候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">「今天系列」还完全排不上号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要问全网人民最讨厌哪句话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">必然是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>——在吗？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200729/77be75ea71064632a09d3654f10ccb3b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于没钱没时间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不想额外社交的当代社畜来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最怕收到来自不熟朋友的突然问候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>因为这句话的潜台词</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>大多时候都是“负面”的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“我想找你借钱”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“有个东西你能帮我顺手做了吗”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“我要结婚了，虽然不熟但你得来”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200729/e0867aa2201a43d789bd470aeb86b62d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“在吗”就相当于一颗不定时炸弹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">深深地埋在对话当中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你回或不回</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它就摆在那里，让你难受</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200729/15abff1229424386ae8551b3620189e3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“在吗”的变式还有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“在？” “在不在？”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">讨厌程度尤胜本体</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果想要当一名有礼貌的网瘾少年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">请一定要戒除“在吗？”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了直戳心窝和没营养之外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有一些问候语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那真的是令人迷惑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200729/499a7570479242d29d55ec24ad893276.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然大家加完好友的第一件事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是翻朋友圈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但也不必说出来的好吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">况且这种自以为是的优越感和幽默</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就更令人反感了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200729/59a9c189ffcf4ff5bffb7b6ff06ac14a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有一些朋友</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">喜欢用“亲爱的、宝贝”替代“你好”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为一种对外社交的问候语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">体现出自己的热情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200729/2153b87f9feb4ba8ab24eecb598dd087.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但这种句式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅像极了网店客服</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也恍惚间让人以为你是从事公关行业的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">反而会让人产生不适的感觉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200729/6e11bbcdce5b4ddaa075f170f36fc157.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实说到底</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问候语只是一种表达关切的语言</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">并没有对或错的衡量标准</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只要是发自内心的真心话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用什么句式的问候语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实并不重要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">关键在于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你能否从这些语言中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>发现对方的情绪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>能否给出对方需要的关怀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才是交际中语言表达的独特魅力吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200729/358687d7a99a461b8236a44b8c388a70.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▼</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200729/8ad60d5c9e48445d9be8aa4339541153.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你的家乡有哪些常用问候语？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来留言区聊聊吧~</p>
